to the back-end servers.

00:15:10.766 --> 00:15:12.586 A:middle
So this might look a little
bit daunting at first,

00:15:12.886 --> 00:15:15.246 A:middle
but the good news for
game developers is three

00:15:15.246 --> 00:15:16.856 A:middle
of these steps are
