by calling Start Broadcast

00:16:28.446 --> 00:16:32.266 A:middle
on the new RPBroadcastController
instance, that was passed in.

00:16:32.696 --> 00:16:35.156 A:middle
And now we are live.

00:16:35.576 --> 00:16:36.946 A:middle
And since we're live
broadcasting,

00:16:37.266 --> 00:16:39.196 A:middle
we need to clearly
indicate this to the user.

00:16:39.896 --> 00:16:41.696 A:middle
So Olympus Rising
