00:19:35.876 --> 00:19:37.376 A:middle
So let's go back to
that flow diagram.

00:19:37.996 --> 00:19:39.476 A:middle
We've seen that the
gamer is responsible

00:19:39.476 --> 00:19:42.676 A:middle
for initiating the
broadcast, and controlling

00:19:42.676 --> 00:19:44.216 A:middle
when to start and
