to get back to the game.

00:21:34.376 --> 00:21:36.066 A:middle
So, during sign up
it is also required

00:21:36.066 --> 00:21:37.606 A:middle
that the user be shown
terms and conditions

00:21:37.606 --> 00:21:40.756 A:middle
for using the service, and be
provided the ability to accept

00:21:40.956 --> 00:21:42.366 A:middle
or decline those
terms and conditions.

00:21:43.766 --> 00:21:46.806 A:middle
So as we saw earlier, UI
extension is also responsible

